column1: Daily data of meteorological variables monitored at the IAG Meteorological Station in Sao Paulo (WMO station #83004)
column2: except for the variables pblh.m. and ustar.m.s.

column1: pblh.m.: planetary boundary layer height at 12:00 local time (m)
ustar.m.s.: friction velocity at 12:00 local time(m/s)
Insolacao: number of hours of solar radiation (hours)
pwv: total column water vapour at 12:00 local time (kg m-2)
